patch.description:
Incrementally update a stored blueprint.

Payload schema (minimal):
    {
      "nodes": [ { ...NodeSpec... | {"id": "node_id", "type": "__delete__"} ]
    }

post.description:
Kick off a workflow execution.

Expected JSON body::
    {
        "blueprint_id": "...",            # required
        "inputs": {...}                     # optional initial inputs
    }

Create or update a user library asset using semantic memory storage.

- Stores under scope 'library' by default
- Key format: asset:{user_id}:{label}
